    "updated_at": "2025-08-10T18:10:21Z",
    "body": "Indeed, it's either related to `core.precomposeUnicode` or `core.ignoreCase`, while precompose-unicode related transformations are more likely to cause trouble.\n\nIn theory, this is handled correctly from the ground up, but in practice, there are probably plenty of places where issues around this could creep in.\n\nCould we get a test-setup for a reproducer? It should be enough to create a new repository, copy-paste the offending filename, and add it as empty file there. `gix status` should still see it as untracked. *(Strangely, it should also see a seemingly similar file as 'deleted', which isn't the case here.)*",
