    "updated_at": "2025-08-19T03:06:11Z",
    "body": "Can you share how your submodule looks like? What's the (top-level) content of `chest`?\n\n[The code](https://github.com/GitoxideLabs/gitoxide/blob/c3c650448f92bcb27194ce0a51f7d604ce87920d/gix/src/submodule/mod.rs#L385-L388) already checks for this and it shouldn't be possible that the submodule repository then doesn't have a worktree.\n\nIdeally I get a reproducer out of this, so if you are able to setup a new directory that also has this problem that you can zip up and share here, that would be ideal.\n\nThanks again.",
