    "updated_at": "2025-09-04T17:26:51Z",
    "body": "Thanks for sharing!\n\nI'd also really like to get to the bottom of this @karrikuivanen. \n\nMy setup is as follows: `~/.gitconfig` refers to the excludes file:\n\n```gitconfig\n[core]\n        excludesFile = ~/.gitignore\n```\n\nAnd that file contains this:\n\n```\n.idea/\n$.idea/\n\n/.vscode/\n$/.vscode/\n\n/.zed\n\n.DS_Store\n/target/\n\n.cargo/\n$.cargo/\n\n*.iml\n$*.iml\n```\n\nAll this works as expected, and I wonder what kind of setup you are having so that it doesn't work. Thanks again.",
